You are working on harness-company, a Next.js 15 company introduction / portfolio website template.

## Stack
- Next.js 15 (App Router)
- React 19
- TypeScript (strict)
- Tailwind CSS v4 (CSS-first `@theme`, no `tailwind.config.ts`)
- Framer Motion
- Neon (serverless Postgres) — contact form storage, server-side only, optional
- Password-based admin auth (server `ADMIN_PASSWORD` + httpOnly cookie)
- Lucide React (icons)
- Noto Sans KR (placeholder font, swappable in `layout.tsx`)

## Key Conventions

### Content
All site content lives in `src/lib/data.ts`. When the user wants to change text, links, services, testimonials, or contact info, edit this file.

### Colors
There is no `tailwind.config.ts` (Tailwind v4 is CSS-first). Theme tokens live in the `@theme` block of `src/app/globals.css`. The template ships a neutral placeholder palette (Tailwind's built-in `neutral` scale). Add a brand accent by declaring `--color-brand-*` in `@theme`.

### Components
- UI primitives: `src/components/ui/` (Button, Card, AnimatedSection, PageHeader)
- Page sections: `src/components/sections/` (Hero, About, Services, Portfolio, Testimonials, Contact)
- Layout: `src/components/layout/` (Navbar, Footer)
- Admin: `src/components/admin/` (AdminLayout, ContactTable, ProtectedRoute)

### Animations
All sections use `AnimatedSection` wrapper (intersection observer + Framer Motion fade-up).

### Data & Auth (Neon + password)
- DB layer (server-only): `src/lib/db.ts` — Neon client, null-safe when `DATABASE_URL` unset
- Admin auth (server-only): `src/lib/auth.ts` — sha256 session token + httpOnly cookie
- Client fetch helpers: `src/lib/api.ts` — talks to `/api/*` route handlers
- Route handlers: `src/app/api/contact`, `/api/admin/{login,logout,session,contacts}`
- Auth hook: `src/hooks/useAuth.ts` — cookie-session state
- Contact form saves to the `contacts` table via `POST /api/contact`

### File Ownership
| Change | File |
|---|---|
| Site content | `src/lib/data.ts` |
| Colors | `src/app/globals.css` `@theme` block |
| Font | `src/app/layout.tsx` |
| Contact form → DB | `src/lib/db.ts` + `src/app/api/contact/route.ts` |
| Admin auth | `src/lib/auth.ts` + `src/app/api/admin/*` |
| Admin table | `src/components/admin/ContactTable.tsx` |
| Animations | `src/components/ui/AnimatedSection.tsx` |
| DB / admin credentials | `.env.local` (`DATABASE_URL`, `ADMIN_PASSWORD`) |

### Code Style
- Use TypeScript strict mode
- Prefer named exports
- Use `cn()` from `src/lib/utils.ts` for conditional class names
- Icons: import specific icons from `lucide-react`
- All client components must have `'use client'` directive
- Comments at customization points for non-developer users

## Deployment: GitHub → Vercel
1. GitHub push → Vercel 자동 재배포 (main 브랜치)
2. Vercel 환경변수: `.env.example` 키 전부 입력

## DB / 인증: Neon + 비밀번호
- DB: Neon (서버리스 PostgreSQL), `DATABASE_URL` 환경변수. Vercel → Storage → Neon 연동 시 자동 주입.
- `DATABASE_URL` 미설정이어도 빌드/실행 가능 (연락처 폼은 "저장 설정 전", 관리자 표는 빈 상태).
- 관리자 인증: 단일 비밀번호 `ADMIN_PASSWORD`(서버 전용) + httpOnly 세션 쿠키. 별도 사용자 계정 없음.
- DB 접근은 서버 사이드 전용. admin 경로는 robots.ts에서 크롤링 차단됨.

## SEO 설정
- `.env.local`에 `GOOGLE_SITE_VERIFICATION`, `NAVER_SITE_VERIFICATION` 입력
- Google Search Console: https://search.google.com/search-console
- 네이버 서치어드바이저: https://searchadvisor.naver.com
- sitemap.xml / robots.txt 자동 생성됨 (`src/app/sitemap.ts`, `src/app/robots.ts`)
- `public/og-image.png` (1200×630px) 추가 시 SNS 공유 미리보기 활성화

## 도메인 연결 (가비아 → Cloudflare → Vercel)
1. 가비아에서 도메인 구매
2. Cloudflare에 도메인 등록 → 네임서버 2개 복사
3. 가비아 네임서버를 Cloudflare 네임서버로 변경
4. Vercel Settings > Domains에 도메인 추가 → CNAME 값 확인
5. Cloudflare DNS에 CNAME 레코드 추가 (Proxy: DNS only)
6. `.env.local`의 `NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL` 실제 도메인으로 변경 후 재배포
